Class GenericQueryDao<T,PK extends Serializable>

All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericDao<T,PK>
public class GenericQueryDao<T,PK extends Serializable>
extends org.anyframe.query.dao.QueryServiceDaoSupport
implements GenericDao<T,PK>

This class serves as the generic class for all other DAOs using Anyframe QueryService - namely to hold common CRUD methods that they might all use. You should only need to extend this class when your require custom CRUD logic.

Author:
Bryan Noll, modified by SooYeon Park

getPagingList

public org.anyframe.pagination.Page getPagingList(org.anyframe.datatype.SearchVO searchVO)
                                           throws Exception
Generic method to get object list based on search condition and search keyword This method will be mostly overridden by developers to use specific search conditions.

Specified by:
getPagingList in interface GenericDao<T,PK extends Serializable>
Parameters:
searchVO - search condition and search keyword
Returns:
result page object with total count
Query Mapping XML Example: 
  <queryservice>
   <queries>
                <query id="findBoardList" isDynamic="true">
        <statement>
        <![CDATA[
                SELECT 
                        board.BOARD_ID, board.BOARD_DESC, board.BOARD_MASTER_ID, board.BOARD_NAME, board.BOARD_ORDER, board.BOARD_TOPICS, board.REG_DATE 
                FROM BOARD board
                #if ($keywordNum != "")                 
                        WHERE           
                        #if ($condition == "All" || $condition == "")
                                (
                                  board.BOARD_NAME like :keywordStr
                                 #if($isNumeric == "true")
                                        or board.BOARD_ID = {{keywordNum}}  or board.BOARD_MASTER_ID = {{keywordNum}}  or board.BOARD_TOPICS = {{keywordNum}} 
                                 #end
                                )       
                        #elseif($condition == "id.boardId")
                                board.BOARD_ID = {{keywordNum}} 
                        #elseif($condition == "id.boardMasterId")
                                board.BOARD_MASTER_ID = {{keywordNum}}  
                        #elseif($condition == "boardTopics")
                                board.BOARD_TOPICS = {{keywordNum}}     
                        #elseif($condition == "boardName")
                                board.BOARD_NAME like :keywordStr                       
                        #end
                #end                    
                        order by                                                        
                        board.BOARD_ID
        ]]>
        </statement>
        <result class="singleapp1.foundation.sales.dao.Board">            
                <result-mapping column="{BOARD_ID, BOARD_MASTER_ID}" attribute="{id.boardId, id.boardMasterId}"/>
                <result-mapping column="{BOARD_MASTER_ID}" attribute="{boardMaster.boardMasterId}"/>
        </result>                         
    </query>
   </queries>
  </queryservice>
Throws:
Exception - if there is any problem getting object list
